channel.title: Whats Your Favorite Song?
channel.description:
Just post one of your favorite songs. Of course no one has just one song, so just choose one, you can always post another one later if you feel like it. Its always good to post a link to listen to the song :rolleyes:
[url=http://youtube.com/watch?v=8I4nNj1r4uQ]Give It All[/url] - [url=http://myspace.com/riseagainst]Rise Against[/url]
